Juventus drew 0-0 with Monaco at the Stade Louis II on Wednesday night .
Patrice Evra scored the only goal of the game as the French side progressed 1-0 on aggregate .
Former Manchester United full back says the French team could learn from their style of play .
Vincent Kompany was ruled out for 50 days with a hamstring injury .
Paul Pogba is likely to miss the Champions League semi-finals .